replies.txt_content:
根据日志电力时代Mod在更新实体updateEntity()方法后导致服务器停止响应
LightBlockEntity类：https://github.com/dexman545/Ele ... ghtBlockEntity.java
电力时代Electrical Age站内搬运贴：http://www.mcbbs.net/thread-612801-1-1.html
